1
00:01:23,013 --> 00:01:30,469
<i>[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]</i>

2
00:01:31,945 --> 00:01:35,909
<i>[Episode 8]</i>

3
00:01:37,445 --> 00:01:39,485
Pei Shouyue hit the jackpot

4
00:01:41,605 --> 00:01:43,565
when he married you,

5
00:01:44,405 --> 00:01:46,245
Let me be honest,

6
00:01:47,605 --> 00:01:51,285
If you hadn't handled the Pei family estate

7
00:01:52,285 --> 00:01:55,145
so well this time

8
00:01:55,145 --> 00:01:57,685
and made a good name for Lady Wu,

9
00:01:58,325 --> 00:02:00,925
I would have been a lot tougher on you,

10
00:02:03,085 --> 00:02:05,365
and I wouldn't let Pei Shouyue off the hook,

11
00:02:06,125 --> 00:02:07,325
Please rest assured, Madam,

12
00:02:08,005 --> 00:02:10,405
I won't ever forget
how much Lady Wu's helped out,

13
00:02:11,125 --> 00:02:14,205
I'll make sure my husband
remembers his place, too,

14
00:02:17,805 --> 00:02:19,645
I've got to leave now,

15
00:02:19,645 --> 00:02:22,285
Please take good care, Madam and Lady Wu

16
00:02:54,685 --> 00:02:57,405
Liuli, thank you so much,

17
00:02:58,125 --> 00:02:59,605
Please accept a bow from me,

18
00:03:04,805 --> 00:03:06,605
I should be the one thanking you

19
00:03:08,045 --> 00:03:09,725
for being so smart and taking care of things,

20
00:03:10,525 --> 00:03:11,685
After my sister passed away,

21
00:03:13,045 --> 00:03:14,525
my brother-in-law's been really down,

22
00:03:15,445 --> 00:03:17,965
Now that he's got you,

23
00:03:19,405 --> 00:03:22,405
I bet my sister's smiling down on us,

24
00:03:28,605 --> 00:03:32,725
Thanks for getting justice for her,

25
00:03:34,445 --> 00:03:35,885
Not protecting my sister has always been

26
00:03:36,805 --> 00:03:38,805
Shouyue's deepest regret,

27
00:03:39,485 --> 00:03:42,405
I'm not just helping myself today,

28
00:03:43,045 --> 00:03:45,925
but I'm also easing a worry for Shouyue,

29
00:03:50,085 --> 00:03:51,365
I gotta go,

30
00:03:52,045 --> 00:03:53,125
Take care,

31
00:04:19,125 --> 00:04:21,325
Look how gorgeous the sky is, my dear,

32
00:04:21,325 --> 00:04:23,325
The moon's gonna look amazing tonight,

33
00:04:23,325 --> 00:04:24,945
As long as we hurry along the way,

34
00:04:24,945 --> 00:04:26,965
we will soon catch up with Master,

35
00:04:29,085 --> 00:04:30,245
Who said I was going to chase after him?

36
00:04:31,085 --> 00:04:34,045
My uncle's got a whole caravan set up for me
thirty miles from here, just outside town,

37
00:04:35,085 --> 00:04:36,965
We're heading straight to Western Regions
to do some trading,

38
00:04:38,965 --> 00:04:41,485
Let's go to Xizhou,

39
00:04:57,656 --> 00:05:03,186
<i>♫ The heart only wishes
for happiness and peace ♫</i>

40
00:05:04,856 --> 00:05:10,080
<i>♫ Looking into your eyes,
we are deeply attached to each other ♫</i>

41
00:05:11,064 --> 00:05:17,920
<i>♫ The ink of love
depicts those eyes with tenderness ♫</i>

42
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:24,480
<i>♫ Hiding the past at the tip of the brush ♫</i>

43
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:31,872
<i>♫ Dreams softly sing in my ears ♫</i>

44
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:39,085
<i>♫ If my longings become a cocoon ♫</i>

45
00:05:39,768 --> 00:05:46,432
<i>♫ I'll wait for wind and snow
to bury the budding fate ♫</i>

46
00:05:46,432 --> 00:05:53,076
<i>♫ Having no cares,
love has gone astray in the wilderness ♫</i>

47
00:05:53,076 --> 00:05:55,712
<i>♫ We look at each other from a far distance ♫</i>

48
00:05:55,712 --> 00:06:00,256
<i>♫ Written in memories are the words of wisdom ♫</i>

49
00:06:01,565 --> 00:06:04,565
<i>It is said that the couple's fate is deeply
gracious and significant,</i>

50
00:06:05,965 --> 00:06:08,885
<i>Talking about shared burdens,
yet the vows are still far-off,</i>

51
00:06:10,645 --> 00:06:13,485
<i>Every couple is tied by
the karma of their past life,</i>

52
00:06:14,165 --> 00:06:15,685
<i>That's how they become a couple in this life,</i>

53
00:06:17,645 --> 00:06:20,965
<i>If the bond doesn't match,
they will be enemies,</i>

54
00:06:22,045 --> 00:06:25,325
<i>like cats and mice hate each other
and like wolves and sheep in one place,</i>

55
00:06:30,445 --> 00:06:33,805
<i>Since two hearts draft away,
it's hard to return to consensus,</i>

56
00:06:36,565 --> 00:06:39,285
<i>Please hurry and inform all the relatives
we'll return to our respective paths,</i>

57
00:06:41,885 --> 00:06:43,725
<i>I wish that after we part ways,</i>

58
00:06:44,965 --> 00:06:48,605
<i>you will beautify yourself,
with elegant hair and delicate eyebrows,</i>

59
00:06:50,325 --> 00:06:54,605
<i>and marry a high-ranking official
who appreciates your beauty,</i>

60
00:06:55,845 --> 00:06:59,445
<i>Let go of resentment, break free from the past,
and don't harbor animosity towards each other,</i>

61
00:07:06,325 --> 00:07:09,565
<i>Parting ways will bring happiness
to both of us,</i>

62
00:07:11,565 --> 00:07:14,645
<i>I will provide clothing and food
for the next three years,</i>

63
00:07:16,125 --> 00:07:19,245
<i>Wishing you a long and prosperous life
for eternity,</i>

64
00:07:21,765 --> 00:07:24,265
Ever since you left Chang'an,

65
00:07:24,265 --> 00:07:26,185
You drink alcohol every day
as if you were drinking water,

66
00:07:26,185 --> 00:07:27,885
No matter how fine the alcohol, it's no good,

67
00:07:28,885 --> 00:07:31,885
I'm worried that if we continue like this,
your body won't be able to take it,

68
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:50,304
<i>♫ We look at each other from a far distance ♫</i>

69
00:07:50,304 --> 00:07:54,793
<i>♫ Written in memories are the words of wisdom ♫</i>

70
00:07:54,793 --> 00:07:57,472
<i>♫ Traverse the mortal world in misty rain ♫</i>

71
00:07:57,472 --> 00:08:02,003
<i>♫ It's hard to tell from the dark ink stain ♫</i>

72
00:08:02,003 --> 00:08:05,856
<i>♫ Hope that time will dissolve ♫</i>

73
00:08:05,856 --> 00:08:09,591
<i>♫ The chapter of a solemn pledge of love ♫</i>

74
00:08:10,925 --> 00:08:13,445
Hey sis, we should hit the road,

75
00:08:14,125 --> 00:08:15,525
<i>[Liuli's sister, An Sanniang]</i>
I know you are worried about Senior Official Pei,

76
00:08:16,125 --> 00:08:18,205
but we have been traveling non-stop these days,

77
00:08:18,205 --> 00:08:20,005
I'm just worried you might be pushing yourself
too hard,

78
00:08:21,525 --> 00:08:22,685
At least you should eat something,

79
00:08:23,995 --> 00:08:25,581
<i>[Liuli's cousin, Mu Sanlang]</i>

80
00:08:30,085 --> 00:08:32,965
People say that fine wine is a cure for sorrow,

81
00:08:32,965 --> 00:08:34,525
Why do I become more sober the more I drink?

82
00:08:36,405 --> 00:08:38,165
It's because you have such a great tolerance
for alcohol,

83
00:08:39,125 --> 00:08:40,285
Exactly,

84
00:08:40,965 --> 00:08:42,885
But if you wanna talk about getting rid of
the blues, that's easy,

85
00:08:42,885 --> 00:08:45,645
Now, let's turn around
and gallop back to Chang'an,

86
00:08:45,645 --> 00:08:47,765
Then, take Madam with us to Xizhou,

87
00:08:48,925 --> 00:08:52,325
Doing that will just wash all those worries

88
00:08:52,845 --> 00:08:54,365
out of your heart,

89
00:08:54,365 --> 00:08:55,525
Not to mention, Master,

90
00:08:55,525 --> 00:08:56,785
we've been on this journey together

91
00:08:56,785 --> 00:08:58,325
with no big hassles or dangers,

92
00:08:58,885 --> 00:08:59,925
Maybe you're just overthinking things a bit?

93
00:09:00,605 --> 00:09:04,565
The spot we're headed to is basically
the wild place of the country,

94
00:09:08,525 --> 00:09:11,965
Sister, I am now a stranger
to Senior Official Pei,

95
00:09:12,605 --> 00:09:13,605
The rush is more
because I've always been drawn to Xizhou

96
00:09:13,605 --> 00:09:16,205
since I was a kid,

97
00:09:16,925 --> 00:09:19,605
That's where my mom's from,
with all that wide-open space,

98
00:09:21,485 --> 00:09:23,485
I wanna tag along with you
and get into the merchant game out there,

99
00:09:23,485 --> 00:09:25,965
Perhaps I'll even
make a significant accomplishment,

100
00:09:26,485 --> 00:09:28,705
Ok, if you say so,

101
00:09:28,705 --> 00:09:29,885
However, there's one thing,

102
00:09:30,445 --> 00:09:32,745
If your body can't handle it,
you have to tell me,

103
00:09:32,745 --> 00:09:33,765
Don't be out there acting all tough,

104
00:09:34,485 --> 00:09:37,425
Don't mention Pei Xingjian anymore,

105
00:09:37,425 --> 00:09:39,025
It's really bringing everyone down,

106
00:09:39,025 --> 00:09:40,865
He is so heartless and unrighteous,

107
00:09:40,865 --> 00:09:42,165
What's this about leaving a divorce letter?

108
00:09:43,445 --> 00:09:45,005
Liuli, what else were you expecting?

109
00:09:45,765 --> 00:09:47,725
In Xizhou, there are plenty of fine young men

110
00:09:49,765 --> 00:09:51,085
You'll find someone way better!

111
00:09:52,165 --> 00:09:54,225
We have grown up together,

112
00:09:54,225 --> 00:09:55,525
Please zip it with the comments,

113
00:09:56,365 --> 00:09:57,405
So as not to trouble you,

114
00:10:02,005 --> 00:10:03,925
Do you know why I left a divorce letter,

115
00:10:04,645 --> 00:10:06,445
Please enlighten me, Master,

116
00:10:07,365 --> 00:10:08,965
Only by doing this can I sever ties with her,

117
00:10:10,205 --> 00:10:12,805
Then, Lady Wu and Madam Yang

118
00:10:12,805 --> 00:10:14,485
would not get angry with her because of me,

119
00:10:15,365 --> 00:10:18,845
Also, I have already discussed this with Liuli,

120
00:10:20,245 --> 00:10:23,245
We let go of the Luoyang property for cheap
to the Princess,

121
00:10:24,725 --> 00:10:26,405
Without the burden of me and the lands,

122
00:10:27,565 --> 00:10:31,685
Only then could she truly live
a free and comfortable life in Chang'an,

123
00:10:32,805 --> 00:10:34,965
But Master, life doesn't always go as planned,

124
00:10:34,965 --> 00:10:37,925
What if we end up back in Chang'an
in two years?

125
00:10:37,925 --> 00:10:39,445
- What if Madam--
- Two years?

126
00:10:41,205 --> 00:10:43,565
Don't even think about going back
without five to ten years,

127
00:10:44,645 --> 00:10:45,952
No,

128
00:10:47,445 --> 00:10:50,205
Maybe I'll never be able to return to Chang'an
in this lifetime,

129
00:10:55,925 --> 00:10:57,665
It's just my luck

130
00:10:57,665 --> 00:10:58,885
dragging you down,

131
00:11:01,845 --> 00:11:03,445
I should really stop getting others involved,

132
00:11:03,445 --> 00:11:07,325
You sound truly resolute,

133
00:11:07,325 --> 00:11:08,905
but we're moving so slowly,

134
00:11:08,905 --> 00:11:10,205
Who are we waiting on?

135
00:11:29,611 --> 00:11:34,624
<i>[Yunwei Hotel]</i>

136
00:12:16,445 --> 00:12:18,605
You have already tasted the punch of me,

137
00:12:19,925 --> 00:12:21,005
If you feel it's not strong enough,

138
00:12:22,205 --> 00:12:23,565
you can try some of my other moves again,

139
00:12:27,005 --> 00:12:31,245
A proud wolf will never give in
to a vicious dog,

140
00:12:34,445 --> 00:12:38,285
You better figure out where you stand,

141
00:12:39,365 --> 00:12:40,485
A lowly slave girl,

142
00:12:40,485 --> 00:12:43,285
Forget about having
a high-status or fancy family,

143
00:12:43,885 --> 00:12:45,405
Your name is now Ahong,

144
00:12:46,245 --> 00:12:47,685
I hope you remember it firmly,

145
00:14:05,015 --> 00:14:08,704
<i>[Son of Anxi Duhu Qu Zhizhan,
Si Ma of Xizhou, Qu Chongyu]</i>

146
00:14:10,485 --> 00:14:11,552
Have a sit,

147
00:14:13,784 --> 00:14:16,295
<i>[Brother-in-law of Qu Chongyu, Wang Junmeng]</i>

148
00:14:35,925 --> 00:14:37,405
I admire your courage,

149
00:14:40,405 --> 00:14:41,805
but you can't take things too far,

150
00:14:42,645 --> 00:14:43,805
This is your last warning,

151
00:14:45,725 --> 00:14:47,285
Don't push my limits,

152
00:14:48,205 --> 00:14:49,664
because trust me,

153
00:14:52,645 --> 00:14:54,445
you don't want to deal with what comes next,

154
00:14:59,805 --> 00:15:01,405
You are a coward,

155
00:15:07,685 --> 00:15:08,928
Coward,

156
00:15:25,285 --> 00:15:28,125
I said it was your last warning,

157
00:15:52,965 --> 00:15:54,176
Thank you very much,

158
00:15:56,205 --> 00:15:57,216
Stop,

159
00:16:01,125 --> 00:16:04,965
I am Mi Dalang, doing the female slave trade,
It's a pleasure to meet you,

160
00:16:05,685 --> 00:16:06,752
Pei Jiu,

161
00:16:09,365 --> 00:16:11,005
Mr, Pei,

162
00:16:11,005 --> 00:16:12,645
You stepped in to save this female slave,

163
00:16:13,685 --> 00:16:16,325
Do you have the intention to buy her?

164
00:16:16,965 --> 00:16:18,165
What are you doing?

165
00:16:18,165 --> 00:16:20,925
Let me tell you,
Master is a government official,

166
00:16:21,525 --> 00:16:22,765
If you dare to be presumptuous again,

167
00:16:23,485 --> 00:16:25,005
I will call the soldiers to catch you,

168
00:16:26,725 --> 00:16:28,685
Cheng, watch your manner,

169
00:16:29,365 --> 00:16:31,205
Go tie the horses properly,

170
00:16:31,205 --> 00:16:32,445
- Master…
- It's okay,

171
00:16:32,965 --> 00:16:35,185
- It's just a misunderstanding,
- Yes, you're right,

172
00:16:35,185 --> 00:16:37,685
It's just a misunderstanding, Allow me,

173
00:16:39,605 --> 00:16:42,725
Dear guests, it's cold and windy outside,

174
00:16:42,725 --> 00:16:44,285
Let's chat indoors,

175
00:16:48,045 --> 00:16:49,465
We've got some great wine,

176
00:16:49,465 --> 00:16:51,705
The taste is sweet and has a long aftertaste,

177
00:16:51,705 --> 00:16:53,645
Let's all have some to warm up,

178
00:16:55,045 --> 00:16:56,045
What are we waiting for then?

179
00:16:56,045 --> 00:16:57,205
Let's go inside and have some,

180
00:16:57,205 --> 00:16:58,525
After you, Mr, Pei,

181
00:17:02,205 --> 00:17:05,645
Don't let this female slave spoil our mood,

182
00:17:06,645 --> 00:17:08,205
- Yelun,
- Yes,

183
00:17:08,205 --> 00:17:09,405
Lock her in the stable,

184
00:17:10,165 --> 00:17:11,425
Don't give her food tonight,

185
00:17:11,425 --> 00:17:12,805
Yes, sir,

186
00:17:12,805 --> 00:17:14,085
Mr, Pei, please come in,

187
00:17:18,285 --> 00:17:19,392
After you,

188
00:17:24,125 --> 00:17:25,472
Welcome,

189
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:29,005
Sir, are you here for a meal
or for a stay this time?

190
00:17:29,005 --> 00:17:30,525
Not for staying,

191
00:17:30,525 --> 00:17:32,665
I heard that your place is full of fine wine
from Chang'an,

192
00:17:32,665 --> 00:17:33,725
so I came here,

193
00:17:33,725 --> 00:17:35,765
That's right, Welcome,

194
00:17:36,285 --> 00:17:38,365
So Mr, Pei is also a wine lover,

195
00:17:57,885 --> 00:18:00,925
I am also a wine lover, How about--

196
00:18:00,925 --> 00:18:02,005
Mr, Pei prefers quietness,

197
00:18:02,925 --> 00:18:03,965
He likes drinking by himself,

198
00:18:06,885 --> 00:18:08,160
Cheng,

199
00:18:10,125 --> 00:18:11,485
Thank you for your hospitality,

200
00:18:12,205 --> 00:18:14,365
However, I have always preferred to be alone,

201
00:18:15,365 --> 00:18:16,605
I hope for your understanding,

202
00:18:16,605 --> 00:18:18,205
Well, that's all right then,

203
00:18:35,005 --> 00:18:36,325
Take a seat, Cheng,

204
00:18:41,925 --> 00:18:44,165
Today you're lucky, having escaped death,

205
00:18:45,765 --> 00:18:47,085
But don't get too happy too soon,

206
00:18:48,205 --> 00:18:50,525
Clearly, that weak man didn't want to buy you,

207
00:18:51,205 --> 00:18:53,045
You'll see how I'll deal with you
after they leave,

208
00:18:54,805 --> 00:18:57,005
Just kill me,

209
00:18:57,605 --> 00:18:59,285
Bitch,

210
00:18:59,285 --> 00:19:00,512
Wait a moment,

211
00:19:02,645 --> 00:19:03,936
What is this?

212
00:19:04,605 --> 00:19:06,305
This is freshly cooked mutton soup,

213
00:19:06,305 --> 00:19:07,945
The sheep was freshly slaughtered
in the kitchen today,

214
00:19:07,945 --> 00:19:09,845
The meat in this soup is extremely fresh,

215
00:19:10,765 --> 00:19:11,825
Then you have a look at

216
00:19:11,825 --> 00:19:13,088
that table

217
00:19:15,005 --> 00:19:16,544
and then take another look at this table,

218
00:19:17,165 --> 00:19:18,464
What's all this?

219
00:19:19,285 --> 00:19:20,768
Sir…

220
00:19:22,205 --> 00:19:23,488
Cheng,

221
00:19:26,365 --> 00:19:27,385
Master,

222
00:19:27,385 --> 00:19:29,025
They're really treating us unfairly,

223
00:19:29,025 --> 00:19:31,525
Do they think we have no money?

224
00:19:32,245 --> 00:19:33,885
No, No, No,

225
00:19:33,885 --> 00:19:37,805
Such differential treatment
is simply too outrageous,

226
00:19:40,325 --> 00:19:41,725
It's a misunderstanding!

227
00:19:42,645 --> 00:19:44,165
Sir,

228
00:19:44,165 --> 00:19:47,185
the food for those two guests was brought
by themselves,

229
00:19:47,185 --> 00:19:48,905
My little shop is in the wilderness,

230
00:19:48,905 --> 00:19:52,445
How could we possibly provide such
precious and exquisite delicacies here?

231
00:20:00,285 --> 00:20:02,405
<i>All of these are popular dishes in Chang'an,</i>

232
00:20:03,205 --> 00:20:05,285
<i>and they are all coveted
by the elite and noble families,</i>

233
00:20:06,085 --> 00:20:07,485
<i>Although they are nothing surprising
in Chang'an,</i>

234
00:20:08,725 --> 00:20:11,045
<i>this place is thousands of miles away
from Chang'an,</i>

235
00:20:13,445 --> 00:20:16,645
<i>From his attire, this man is clearly a person
from the West,</i>

236
00:20:17,245 --> 00:20:20,485
<i>but his temperament presents him
as a person of high society from Chang'an,</i>

237
00:20:21,685 --> 00:20:25,645
<i>His demeanor is calm and collected,
relaxed yet extraordinary,</i>

238
00:20:26,365 --> 00:20:27,465
<i>How would such a person</i>

239
00:20:27,465 --> 00:20:29,805
<i>appear in this wilderness tavern?</i>

240
00:20:33,485 --> 00:20:36,725
Have you heard about that troublemaker
everyone in Chang'an is talking about?

241
00:20:36,725 --> 00:20:38,085
Do you mean Pei Xingjian?

242
00:20:38,085 --> 00:20:39,945
He has become arrogant because of favoritism,

243
00:20:39,945 --> 00:20:44,085
He criticized the forbidden areas and even said
the chaos of the nation would start from this,

244
00:20:44,645 --> 00:20:46,445
His Majesty was furious,

245
00:20:46,445 --> 00:20:50,045
he got knocked down and sent to Xizhou,

246
00:21:29,485 --> 00:21:30,976
I also heard that

247
00:21:31,565 --> 00:21:34,525
this person is arrogant because of his talent,

248
00:21:34,525 --> 00:21:35,865
Relying on the Emperor's favor,

249
00:21:35,865 --> 00:21:38,405
he even disregards the elders of his family,

250
00:21:40,005 --> 00:21:42,165
This person has a corrupt character,

251
00:21:42,165 --> 00:21:45,445
He loves wine like life
and is greedy and lustful,

252
00:21:46,405 --> 00:21:48,725
If such a person came to Xizhou,

253
00:21:48,725 --> 00:21:52,885
it would be like
one rotten apple spoils the whole barrel,

254
00:21:54,405 --> 00:21:55,520
Excuse me,

255
00:21:56,725 --> 00:21:57,745
another pot of wine, please,

256
00:21:57,745 --> 00:21:59,200
Alright,

257
00:22:45,525 --> 00:22:47,485
You can really hold your liquor,

258
00:22:48,485 --> 00:22:49,645
It's because your wine is brewed so well,

259
00:22:50,165 --> 00:22:53,205
It's even more fragrant than the wine
I buy in Chang'an,

260
00:22:53,925 --> 00:22:55,445
You flatter me, Enjoy,

261
00:22:56,125 --> 00:22:57,472
Enjoy,

262
00:22:59,085 --> 00:23:01,885
Do you often go to the West Market?

263
00:23:05,125 --> 00:23:06,565
When I'm not on duty,

264
00:23:07,605 --> 00:23:09,125
I tend to go there every two or three days,

265
00:23:10,805 --> 00:23:13,365
What kind of position do you hold?

266
00:23:14,885 --> 00:23:17,565
I'm just a minor official,
not worth mentioning,

267
00:23:19,965 --> 00:23:21,785
So it turns out
that you are from the government,

268
00:23:21,785 --> 00:23:23,725
My bad,

269
00:23:27,845 --> 00:23:30,165
I heard that your last name is also Pei,

270
00:23:34,245 --> 00:23:35,525
That's quite a coincidence,

271
00:23:47,285 --> 00:23:49,525
I am so boring,

272
00:23:49,525 --> 00:23:50,545
Yelun

273
00:23:50,545 --> 00:23:52,385
- Keep an eye on them,
- Okay,

274
00:23:52,385 --> 00:23:53,845
I need to use the restroom,

275
00:24:13,325 --> 00:24:15,965
Such a pity, It was so close,

276
00:24:18,605 --> 00:24:20,565
I have lived here for thirty years,

277
00:24:20,565 --> 00:24:22,405
It's my first time getting hurt by a woman,

278
00:25:11,445 --> 00:25:13,885
Got you now, Do you think you can run away?

279
00:25:30,565 --> 00:25:31,776
Dalang,

280
00:25:37,845 --> 00:25:38,965
Why did you save him?

281
00:25:39,845 --> 00:25:43,325
This man has committed many misdeeds and
has persecuted so many respectable women,

282
00:25:45,725 --> 00:25:47,168
The one I saved is you,

283
00:25:53,965 --> 00:25:54,965
Master, are you alright?

284
00:25:55,565 --> 00:25:56,640
I'm fine,

285
00:25:57,165 --> 00:26:00,525
I am eternally grateful to you, Mr, Pei,
for saving my life,

286
00:26:01,045 --> 00:26:04,005
Like I said, I was saving her,
You don't need to thank me,

287
00:26:04,005 --> 00:26:05,568
I don't need your help,

288
00:26:06,205 --> 00:26:09,405
No matter what, you saved my life,

289
00:26:10,245 --> 00:26:12,025
If you need me in the future,

290
00:26:12,025 --> 00:26:13,485
just give the order anytime,

291
00:26:14,765 --> 00:26:16,405
How do you plan to deal with this female slave?

292
00:26:18,445 --> 00:26:19,805
If you like her,

293
00:26:19,805 --> 00:26:21,605
I can give her to you,

294
00:26:24,565 --> 00:26:25,925
I've said the descendants of the wolf

295
00:26:25,925 --> 00:26:29,365
will never be slaves,

296
00:26:30,445 --> 00:26:31,712
If you don't want her,

297
00:26:32,765 --> 00:26:34,005
I can't keep her either,

298
00:26:35,885 --> 00:26:40,125
Even if I die, I won't let you manipulate me,

299
00:26:49,325 --> 00:26:50,645
Even ants fight for survival,

300
00:26:50,645 --> 00:26:52,005
Why don't you take care of yourself?

301
00:27:58,005 --> 00:27:59,045
Madam,

302
00:28:22,805 --> 00:28:24,096
Liuli,

303
00:28:25,245 --> 00:28:26,645
You must have mistaken me for someone else,

304
00:28:27,485 --> 00:28:28,685
I don't know you,

305
00:29:15,365 --> 00:29:16,765
Liuli, wait for me,

306
00:29:24,685 --> 00:29:25,685
Greetings, Sanniang,

307
00:29:27,965 --> 00:29:28,965
That was all a misunderstanding,

308
00:29:30,125 --> 00:29:31,405
Please let me explain,

309
00:29:31,925 --> 00:29:33,205
Senior Official Pei, please don't be like this,

310
00:29:33,925 --> 00:29:35,405
You don't have to be so polite,

311
00:29:35,925 --> 00:29:38,885
Moreover, there is no need
for you to explain to me,

312
00:29:43,165 --> 00:29:44,285
What's going on?

313
00:29:47,565 --> 00:29:48,928
I don't know,

314
00:29:56,005 --> 00:29:57,605
My lady, you were traveling day and night

315
00:29:58,125 --> 00:29:59,605
to see Master as early as possible,

316
00:30:00,165 --> 00:30:01,605
I didn't expect him to be so excessive,

317
00:30:09,125 --> 00:30:12,065
Tan, you are becoming more and more unruly,

318
00:30:12,065 --> 00:30:14,245
Is Master someone you can casually comment on?

319
00:30:14,245 --> 00:30:15,985
I'm just distressed for you,

320
00:30:15,985 --> 00:30:17,325
I'm feeling indignant on behalf of you,

321
00:30:18,525 --> 00:30:21,485
Based on my understanding of him, I'm afraid--

322
00:30:25,605 --> 00:30:27,325
Liuli,

323
00:30:27,325 --> 00:30:30,445
What just happened is not as you think,

324
00:30:31,405 --> 00:30:33,005
- I--
- Senior Official Pei, please leave,

325
00:30:33,805 --> 00:30:36,045
Since you have written the divorce letter,
there are no longer any ties between us,

326
00:30:36,605 --> 00:30:37,765
Chancellor Pei, please show some respect,

327
00:30:41,085 --> 00:30:42,325
- Liuli,
- Mr, Pei,

328
00:30:42,885 --> 00:30:45,565
Mr, Pei, I've been looking for you,

329
00:30:46,365 --> 00:30:50,305
I have prepared a feast
and a performance for you,

330
00:30:50,305 --> 00:30:53,485
Tonight, we two must have a great time,

331
00:30:54,005 --> 00:30:55,085
Let's go, Let's go,

332
00:30:55,085 --> 00:30:56,985
I've been looking for you for ages,

333
00:30:56,985 --> 00:30:58,165
We must have a great time tonight,

334
00:31:41,605 --> 00:31:42,976
Cheers,

335
00:32:25,485 --> 00:32:26,560
Come on,

336
00:32:29,488 --> 00:32:31,764
