360
00:36:54,165 --> 00:36:55,445
We should wait in Dunhuang,

361
00:36:55,445 --> 00:36:57,885
Why did you insist on coming over here?
What's the point?

362
00:36:58,605 --> 00:36:59,725
I want to see him,

363
00:37:02,245 --> 00:37:03,445
You have seen him now,

364
00:37:04,045 --> 00:37:06,125
Yeah, he's just like this,

365
00:37:06,765 --> 00:37:08,605
Did you see the way he looks at women?

366
00:37:08,605 --> 00:37:12,765
Did you see him mingling with a slave trader?

367
00:37:12,765 --> 00:37:16,245
I really doubt if he knows
that he's the Senior Official,

368
00:37:16,245 --> 00:37:18,465
Do you think the man you just saw

369
00:37:18,465 --> 00:37:20,405
is what Pei Xingjian is really like?

370
00:37:21,645 --> 00:37:23,085
Whether it's real or not, I don't care,

371
00:37:23,085 --> 00:37:24,245
I am not his wife anyway,

372
00:37:24,245 --> 00:37:25,565
Anyway, the Pei Xingjian I see is

373
00:37:25,565 --> 00:37:28,265
this person standing outside, That's all,

374
00:37:28,265 --> 00:37:29,725
Don't judge a book by its cover,

375
00:37:30,965 --> 00:37:35,045
Mi Dalang is a well-known slave trader
in Xizhou,

376
00:37:36,765 --> 00:37:39,925
He is familiar with the local people
and has deep connections,

377
00:37:40,845 --> 00:37:41,925
So what?

378
00:37:42,925 --> 00:37:46,885
I find this Senior Official Pei
quite interesting,

379
00:37:49,525 --> 00:37:52,485
Fine, whatever you say,

380
00:37:54,085 --> 00:37:56,125
The Tang army is going to deploy troops
to Western Regions,

381
00:38:22,285 --> 00:38:23,680
Thank you,

382
00:38:25,365 --> 00:38:26,624
My pleasure,

383
00:38:27,645 --> 00:38:29,885
I cannot bear this honor,

384
00:38:30,925 --> 00:38:32,485
I hope you can show some respect from now on

385
00:38:33,005 --> 00:38:34,125
to avoid embarrassment,

386
00:38:35,165 --> 00:38:38,845
Liuli, are you angry with me?

387
00:38:39,805 --> 00:38:40,925
I know it was my fault,

388
00:38:40,925 --> 00:38:42,245
Senior Official Pei, please don't say that,

389
00:38:43,165 --> 00:38:44,685
How dare a person like me get angry with you?

390
00:38:45,885 --> 00:38:48,205
In the future,
I still need to establish myself in Xizhou,

391
00:38:49,045 --> 00:38:51,325
I may have to rely on
the wise administration of yours,

392
00:38:52,245 --> 00:38:54,525
Our fortuitous meeting today is nothing
more than a coincidence,

393
00:38:55,645 --> 00:38:57,165
You don't need to worry about it,

394
00:38:59,245 --> 00:39:00,768
Liuli,

395
00:39:03,165 --> 00:39:04,445
it is all my fault,

396
00:39:06,085 --> 00:39:07,325
I have wronged you,

397
00:39:08,005 --> 00:39:09,005
I underestimated you

398
00:39:11,765 --> 00:39:13,445
