399
00:39:15,405 --> 00:39:17,045
Even if you never look at me again from now on,

400
00:39:18,885 --> 00:39:20,565
I will never let you suffer in that way,

401
00:39:21,085 --> 00:39:22,560
Senior Official Pei,

402
00:39:23,325 --> 00:39:24,845
you have never looked down on me,

403
00:39:25,565 --> 00:39:26,685
Instead, you have overestimated me by

404
00:39:28,245 --> 00:39:29,965
