as if I were at ease,

407
00:39:36,965 --> 00:39:39,885
But the truth is I'm carefree
and don't have big ambitions,

408
00:39:40,925 --> 00:39:43,865
All I want is to not be controlled by others

409
00:39:43,865 --> 00:39:44,965
