all the scheming and deceit,

410
00:39:48,736 --> 00:39:49,885
Liuli…

411
00:39:49,885 --> 00:39:51,445
Liuli wasn't of noble birth to begin with,

412
00:39:52,605 --> 00:39:54,205
but I never saw myself as inferior

413
00:39:55,445 --> 00:39:57,685
