414
00:39:58,645 --> 00:40:03,325
I came to Xizhou because this vast land here
is enough to satisfy me,

415
00:40:05,085 --> 00:40:06,645
It has nothing to do with you,
Senior Official Pei,

416
00:40:07,925 --> 00:40:09,405
Please don't overthink about it,

417
00:40:15,685 --> 00:40:17,125
From the moment I saw you today,

418
00:40:20,045 --> 00:40:21,485
I realized that I was terribly wrong,

419
00:40:23,285 --> 00:40:24,405
but I never imagined

420
00:40:26,005 --> 00:40:27,485
