421
00:40:29,405 --> 00:40:30,485
You have every right to be angry with me,

422
00:40:32,885 --> 00:40:34,285
I judged you with a petty mind,

423
00:40:35,405 --> 00:40:37,965
I should not have had any expectations of you,

424
00:40:46,205 --> 00:40:47,725
Actually, I not only belittled you

425
00:40:49,965 --> 00:40:51,245
